urdu transliteration text:
Thi Ye Bano Ki Fughan Dunya May Reh Kar Kya Karoon
Maut Ne Barbad Kardala Mera Ghar Kya Karoon
@HujjatELC

@HujjatELC
Hai Rage Jaa Ke Liye Har Sans Nashtar Kya Karoon
Hasrato Ka Dil May Ek Barpa Hai Mehshar Kya Karoon

Ay Mere Noore Nazar Tumko Agar Paungi Mai
Dekhlena Raat Bhar Seene Se Liptaungi Mai
@HujjatELC

Surk Phoolon Se Chaman Gulshan Ke Mehkaungi Mai
Ab Na Bhejungi Tumhay Mai Ghar Se Baahar Kya Karoon
@HujjatELC

Tum Samajhte Ho Yahan Se Apne Ghar Jaungi Mai
Chor Kar Tanha Tumhay Beta Kidhar Jaungi Mai
@HujjatELC

Qabr Se Takrake Sar Jangal May Mar Jaungi Mai
Phayr Loon Kyon Na Gale Par Apne Khanjar Kya Karoon
@HujjatELC

Kuch Nahi Tumko Khabar Sheh Ka Makaan Loota Gaya
Sayedde Abrar Ka Ran May Makaan Loota Gaya
@HujjatELC

Dashte Ghurbat May Hussaini Kaarwan Loota Gaya
Ab Na Akbar Hai Na Abbase Dilawar Kya Karoon
@HujjatELC

Tum Chale Maidan May Kaise Teer Khane Ke Liye
Ab Tumhay Turbat Se Gehware May Laakar Kya Karoon
@HujjatELC
